    font-size:14px;
    color:#374151
    line-height:1.6;">
    Your account has been successfully created!
    <br><br>
    Please use the one-time password (OTP) below to verify your email address:
</p>

<div style="margin:24px 0;
    padding:16px;
    background:#f9fafb;
    border:1px dashed #d1d5db;
    border-radius:8px;
    text-align:center;">
    
    <p style="margin:0 0 8px;
    font-size:12px;
    color:#6b7280;
